{
  "text": "Plasmid pMTEV contains the TEV genome [CITATION_1] and was a generous gift by Dr J.-A. Daròs. The TEV genome used to generate this clone has been isolated from Nicotiana tabacum [CITATION_2] , and its sequence is published elsewhere [CITATION_3] . A stock of infected tissue was generated before starting the evolution experiment (for details, see supplementary material, Supplementary Material online).",
  "correct_citation": {
